2002-07-08 22:22  mitch

	* examples/playlist.gondwana.xml, src/blccc.c, src/blccc.h,
	  src/bleffects.c, src/bleffects.h, src/blmovie-blm.c,
	  src/blmovie.c, src/blmovie.h, src/blplaylist-parse.c,
